definitions.definition: A device which suppresses something, especially an electronic or mechanical device.

subdefinitions.definition: A device added to the barrel of a firearm which reduces the noise and flash generated by firing the weapon.

definitions.definition: A person who suppresses others, a tyrant .
A gene that suppresses the effect of another through epistasis .
